songs.title: I’m Gone
songs.lyrics:

Go back, tell me what I know
Tell me what I know
Tell me what I know
Trully only one way to go
One way to go
One way to go
Help me say they coming back (yeah)
Say they coming back
Don't even wanna check
But my heart is up my chest
Now if (yeah)
I'm gone, I'm gone, I'm gone (yeah, yeah)

[Outro]
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah
Yeah, yeah, yeah
